  "description": "A vibrant and dramatic sunset over a coastal landscape. The sky is filled with intensely colored stratocumulus clouds, showcasing fiery shades of orange and red, blending into deep purples and pinks higher up. The clouds are arranged in horizontal bands, creating a dynamic and textured pattern. Silhouetted hills and distant cityscapes are visible along the horizon line, suggesting a location near a bay or ocean. Dark, leafy trees frame the edges of the image, adding depth and a sense of foreground. The overall effect is one of breathtaking natural beauty and atmospheric grandeur.",
